snippet.textDisplay:
O Musk-williow, scattering fragnance
O sweet breeze of the early morning 
O you who cures ills,O you with the breath of jesus 
O consoler of the grief-stricken
O auspicious Messenger
İ beg you in the name of that same fragnance 
O morning breeze ,if you go to that sacred land someday
Present my greetings to the blessed grave💘💘💘💘
Ya Muhammed  Mustafa 💖💖💖
ALLAH HU AKBAR
